cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and image processing, specifically face reenactment. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel learning framework, which involves disentangling and composing appearance and shape information, indicating a potential fit for the machine learning category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of encoders and decoders, which are common in deep learning, suggesting a possible fit for cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves image manipulation and synthesis, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.GR (Graphics).
